NAD+BA+5049000221:ZZZ+MAERSK NEW ZEALAND LTD'
NAD+CZ+5049000221:ZZZ+MAERSK NEW ZEALAND LTD'
NAD+CA+MAE:172:20'
GID+1'
FTX+AAA+++MISCELLANEOUS PRODUCTS'
