NAD+CA+MAE:172:20'
GID+1'
FTX+AAA+++MISCELLANEOUS GOODS'
EQD+CN++" &amp; _isoType &amp; ":102:5+1+2+" &amp; _mt &amp; "'
RFF+BN:" &amp; _release &amp; "'
EQN+" &amp; _quantity &amp; "'
TMD+3++2'
DTM+201:" &amp; strTS1 &amp; ":203'
